  • Constructor Details

    • Customer

      public Customer(int customerId, String customerName, String customerAddress, String customerPostalCode, String customerPhoneNumber, int divisionId, String customerDivisionName, String customerCountryName, LocalDateTime createDate)
      Constructs a Customer object with the specified parameters.
      Parameters:
      customerId - The Id for the customer.
      customerName - The name of the customer.
      customerAddress - The address of the customer.
      customerPostalCode - The postal code of the customer.
      customerPhoneNumber - The phone number of the customer.
      divisionId - The Id of the division to which the customer belongs.
      customerDivisionName - The name of the division to which the customer belongs.
      customerCountryName - The name of the country to which the customer belongs.
      createDate - The date and time when the customer was created.
